To configure:
  $ ./configure
or
  $ ./configure --prefix=/path/to/root
or
  $ ./configure --site_scm_dir=/path/to/dest --site_scm_go_dir=/dummy


To install only sources in /path/to/dest:
  $ ./configure --site_scm_dir=/path/to/dest --site_scm_go_dir=/dummy
  $ make install-srcs

You must specify site_scm_go_dir to avoid use of `guile'.

